==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Smasher
<hw>Smash"er</hw> <pr>(sm⟦acr⟧sh"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that which, smashes or breaks things to
pieces.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Anything very large or extraordinary.</def>
<mark>[Slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>One who passes counterfeit coin.</def> <mark>[Cant,
Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Smatch</ent>⟦br⟧
